com.stremebase.dal

Class TableRelation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.stremebase.dal.TableRelation

  • public class TableRelation
extends Object
    Relates keys from two tables. Also indexes the inverted direction if needed. Tables will ensure that removals are cascaded to here.

    Possible relation types found in DB: DB.ONE_TO_ONE, DB.ONE_TO_MANY, DB.MANY_TO_ONE, DB.MANY_TO_MANY

    Cannot relate keys from more than two tables.

    Author:
    olli
